        "@value": "<p>We are excited to have you join us for the 2026 Spring Recital. We are proud to showcase\nwhat our students have been working on all year and all of their talents.\n</p> \n\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {\n    display: block!important;\n}\n</style>"
